      "review_summary": "The PR changes tools-manager to read GitHub latest-release JSON through a 1 MiB `readResponseWithLimit` cap, adds helper-level proof tests, and commits a standalone evidence script.\n\nPR surface: Source +6, Tests +98, Other +74. Total +178 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main and `v2026.6.10` both read tools-manager GitHub latest-release success bodies through `response.json()`, so the unbounded path is source-reproducible without running an OOM scenario.",
